name: pythreejs
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
    name: pythreejs
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: pythreejs-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pythreejs/pythreejs-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: 7ccfe87baa0fa882a0965d0abd4d0de5

build:
    number: 1
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
        - jupyter
    run:
        - python
        - ipywidgets >=5.1.5

test:
    imports:
        - pythreejs

about:
    home: https://github.com/jovyan/pythreejs
    license: BSD 3-Clause
    summary: A Python / ThreeJS bridge utilizing the Jupyter widget infrastructure.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - SylvainCorlay
    - jasongrout

about.summary: A Python / ThreeJS bridge utilizing the Jupyter widget infrastructure.
